1053
01:35:02.20 --> 01:35:13.20
But for him to yell out, you know, it was a it was a double whammy because in one way he's saying to the guys, I'm with you guys.

1054
01:35:13.20 --> 01:35:19.20
And the other way he was saying to the enemy, I ain't going to do what you want me to do.

1055
01:35:19.20 --> 01:35:23.20
So it was a double whammy and it was very powerful, very powerful.

1056
01:35:23.20 --> 01:35:28.20
And, you know, he was always kind of a quick thinker to make trouble.

1057
01:35:28.20 --> 01:35:30.20
That was part of his reputation.

1058
01:35:30.20 --> 01:35:33.20
Doesn't he like last at the Naval Academy in his class or something like this?

1059
01:35:33.20 --> 01:35:35.20
