1078
01:36:46.20 --> 01:36:49.20
Then you can have one in your house, maybe, but you're still going to watch it.

1079
01:36:49.20 --> 01:37:03.20
So, you know, if you get a guy like McCain, who's the last in his class at the Naval Academy and, you know, has a reputation for kind of causing problems, that's exactly the kind of guy you want in these cases.

1080
01:37:03.20 --> 01:37:04.20
Yeah.

1081
01:37:04.20 --> 01:37:15.20
