1082
01:37:15.20 --> 01:37:25.20
go through all the requirements of flight school, go through the training and then become a fighter pilot without having something similar to the other people.

1083
01:37:25.20 --> 01:37:30.20
In fact, there's a book I have, I brought with me today.

1084
01:37:30.20 --> 01:37:37.20
I wish I showed you that, but there are five categories of similarities between fighter pilots.

1085
01:37:37.20 --> 01:37:43.20
And one of them is that they are, they're very aggressive and risk takers, but they're also affiliative.

1086
01:37:43.20 --> 01:37:48.20
They like to be around people so they can tell their war stories to, you know.

1087
01:37:48.20 --> 01:38:01.20
